{"tid":588531,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇識日文巴絲可以幫幫手","createTime":"2018-03-11T09:19:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-12T09:58:29.000Z","uid":16700,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"9c8ee64c9927de478f830810076cffeb590cfb61","tid":588531,"uid":16700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T09:19:45.000Z","msg":"有一句日文 可唔可以幫我 譯一譯<br />\n<br />\n「今日係我老婆生日，可唔可以邀請你同佢講句 生日快樂。」<br />\n<br />\n唔係冇google 過，我自己都有做功課<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但怕會有錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n希望各位巴絲可以幫幫我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\nkyou wa watashi no tsuma tannjoubi da , <br />\n後面個句真係做左功課都搵唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n因為我所知道日文會有敬語個d, 我怕我咁講會好冇禮貌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24ead318e6cc1ca508c00da44b352ef7859ac9da","tid":588531,"uid":76514,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T09:54:20.000Z","msg":"今日は私の妻の誕生日です。<br />\n妻に「誕生日おめでとう」と言ってくれてくださいませんか。<br />\n<br />\nKyou wa watashi no tsuma no tanjoubi desu. <br />\nTsuma ni `tanjoubi omedeto' to ite kurete kudasaimasen ka.<br />\n<br />\n利申得N4 <br />\n你當我幫推 等其他勁啲既巴絲出手啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n巴打好似好錫老婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f12279ebfe984a44a4c114f1ef9bff96a48c7f2b","tid":588531,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":19,"score":-19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T10:00:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"88a3123dade98075a9897d3d793251f1e0241d17","tid":588531,"uid":16724,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"f12279ebfe984a44a4c114f1ef9bff9